00059         NEDElement *get(const std::string& key) const
00060             {std::map<std::string,NEDElement*>::const_iterator it = map.find(key); return it==map.end() ? NULL : it->second;}
00061         void put(const std::string& key, NEDElement *node)
00062             {Assert(!contains(key)); map[key]=node; keys.push_back(key); values.push_back(node);}
00063         int size() const {return keys.size();}
00064         const std::string& key(int i) const {return keys[i];}
00065         NEDElement *value(int i) const {return values[i];}
00066         void putAll(const NEDElementMap& map)
00067             {for (int i=0; i<map.size(); i++) put(map.key(i),map.value(i));}
